{
  "texts": [
    "Water is pumped using P101 and combined with the HCl pumped by P201.",
    "The pH is then measured using sensor AIT201.",
    "However, if the HCl being transported is mislabelled as NaOCl, each is poured into an incorrect tank.",
    "This means the tank holding HCl now holds NaOCl and vice versa.",
    "AIT201 no longer measure the pH of water mixed with HCl, and it instead measures the mix with NaOCl."
  ]
}